          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">
            <span style="background: #e6f7f5; color: #00A699; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;">LIVE</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
